elements.name: Como usuario administrador quiero modificar un post ya publicado para después editar su contenido

steps.name: I click sign in button with selector "button[data-test-button='sign-in']"
I go to the posts section with selector "a[data-test-nav='posts']"
I click in the new post button with selector "a[data-test-new-post-button]"
I enter title "$name_postTitle" into field with selector "textarea[data-test-editor-title-input]"
I click in the Publish button

steps.name: I click in the Continue, final review button with selector "button[data-test-button='continue']"
I click in the Publish post confirm button with selector "button[data-test-button='confirm-publish']"
I go back to the editor section clicking the editor button with selector "button.gh-publish-back-button"
I go back to the list of posts clicking the posts button with selector "a[data-test-link='posts']"
I click the post in order to edit it
I enter title "$name_postTitleModified" into field with selector "textarea[data-test-editor-title-input]"
I update the post by clicking the Update button with selector "button[data-test-button='publish-save']"
I go back to the list of posts clicking the posts button with selector "a[data-test-link='posts']"
I validate that the title of the post was modified successfully with "$$name_postTitleModified"
I send a signal to user 2 containing "Scenario1 complete"
